{"tid":809660,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：筲箕灣Food Angel","createTime":"2018-09-07T10:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T18:13:56.000Z","uid":181719,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df73e66b42f01f5dfa034c75d2ef89f4b3e22cee","tid":809660,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:44:37.000Z","msg":"比個靚分先，5個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好<br />\n味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好少出返工 lunch 嘅食評，但呢間真係高質，同埋佢根本唔做晚市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/183419_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F183419_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8d6782c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/183503_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F183503_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4d6b4bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n脆皮焗豬手配酸菜伴意粉，豬手份量以lunch黎講係霸氣，炸嘅時間拿捏得好，食落夠惹味又唔太乾，咸香恰到好處。酸菜無他特別，就係夠酸，去到膩。意粉有輕微炒過，單獨食都唔失禮，連埋餐包餐湯餐飲，62蚊，係堅好食兼食唔哂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/183739_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F183739_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dd519655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菠菜雞批係同事叫嘅，純粹唔想得一樣野寫，所以搭單講埋，試咗少少，味道中規中矩啫，冇豬手咁出色。份量亦都唔太夠，要連埋餐包餐湯先夠飽喇。"},{"pid":"7a0481fb92e2cc3a9c915104956ffe3e9c38edc1","tid":809660,"uid":106246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"淨係服務態度同啲位都扣到變負分啦"},{"pid":"ee8ad8d45e597d429e5c890d218648e68f79d0b5","tid":809660,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a0481fb92e2cc3a9c915104956ffe3e9c38edc1","tid":809660,"uid":106246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"淨係服務態度同啲位都扣到變負分啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T11:29:51.000Z","msg":"好似openrice有人屌過佢服務差，我去食過3次又冇乜特別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8c305280073b11ca0e65a279df5aeb81488a9a","tid":809660,"uid":106246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee8ad8d45e597d429e5c890d218648e68f79d0b5","tid":809660,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a0481fb92e2cc3a9c915104956ffe3e9c38edc1","tid":809660,"uid":106246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"淨係服務態度同啲位都扣到變負分啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T11:29:51.000Z","msg":"好似openrice有人屌過